        {
          "html": "<div style=\"--color-midnight-core:#000000;--color-ivory-canvas:#ffffff;--color-slate-text:#808080;--color-onyx-layer:#1a1a1a;--color-ghost-white:#f5f5f5;--color-molten-orange:#e2572c;--font-suisse-font:'Inter',sans-serif;background:var(--color-midnight-core);padding:48px 32px;box-sizing:border-box;width:100%;font-family:var(--font-suisse-font);\"><p style=\"margin:0 0 8px 0;font-family:var(--font-suisse-font);font-size:12px;font-weight:400;color:var(--color-molten-orange);letter-spacing:0.006em;text-transform:uppercase;\">Platform Features</p><h2 style=\"margin:0 0 32px 0;font-family:var(--font-suisse-font);font-size:24px;font-weight:400;color:var(--color-ivory-canvas);line-height:1.33;letter-spacing:-0.007em;\">Everything your customers need, embedded in your platform</h2><div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:16px;\"><div style=\"background:var(--color-onyx-layer);border-radius:16px;padding:24px;box-sizing:border-box;\"><div style=\"width:36px;height:36px;background:var(--color-molten-orange);border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:16px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;\"><svg width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 18 18\" fill=\"none\"><rect x=\"2\" y=\"4\" width=\"14\" height=\"10\" rx=\"2\" stroke=\"#000\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><path d=\"M2 8h14\" stroke=\"#000\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/></svg></div><h3 style=\"margin:0 0 8px 0;font-family:var(--font-suisse-font);font-size:16px;font-weight:400;color:var(--color-ivory-canvas);line-height:1.5;\">Embedded Capital</h3><p style=\"margin:0;font-family:var(--font-suisse-font);font-size:13px;font-weight:400;color:var(--color-slate-text);line-height:1.63;\">Give your customers access to fast, flexible capital without ever leaving your platform.</p></div><div style=\"background:var(--color-onyx-layer);border-radius:16px;padding:24px;box-sizing:border-box;\"><div style=\"width:36px;height:36px;background:#1f1f1f;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:16px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;\"><svg width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 18 18\" fill=\"none\"><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"9\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#e2572c\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><path d=\"M9 6v3l2 2\" stroke=\"#e2572c\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg></div><h3 style=\"margin:0 0 8px 0;font-family:var(--font-suisse-font);font-size:16px;font-weight:400;color:var(--color-ivory-canvas);line-height:1.5;\">Revenue Advance</h3><p style=\"margin:0;font-family:var(--font-suisse-font);font-size:13px;font-weight:400;color:var(--color-slate-text);line-height:1.63;\">Unlock future recurring revenue today. Instant advances on contracted income streams.</p></div><div style=\"background:var(--color-onyx-layer);border-radius:16px;padding:24px;box-sizing:border-box;\"><div style=\"width:36px;height:36px;background:#1f1f1f;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:16px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;\"><svg width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 18 18\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M3 9l4 4 8-8\" stroke=\"#e2572c\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></div><h3 style=\"margin:0 0 8px 0;font-family:var(--font-suisse-font);font-size:16px;font-weight:400;color:var(--color-ivory-canvas);line-height:1.5;\">Instant Payouts</h3><p style=\"margin:0;font-family:var(--font-suisse-font);font-size:13px;font-weight:400;color:var(--color-slate-text);line-height:1.63;\">Move money in real time. Let your customers access earnings immediately on demand.</p></div><div style=\"background:var(--color-onyx-layer);border-radius:16px;padding:24px;box-sizing:border-box;\"><div style=\"width:36px;height:36px;background:#1f1f1f;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:16px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;\"><svg width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 18 18\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M9 2v4M9 12v4M2 9h4M12 9h4\" stroke=\"#e2572c\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg></div><h3 style=\"margin:0 0 8px 0;font-family:var(--font-suisse-font);font-size:16px;font-weight:400;color:var(--color-ivory-canvas);line-height:1.5;\">API-First Stack</h3><p style=\"margin:0;font-family:var(--font-suisse-font);font-size:13px;font-weight:400;color:var(--color-slate-text);line-height:1.63;\">Integrate in days with clean APIs and SDKs built for modern development teams.</p></div></div></div>",
